<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Confirmation email</title>
    
</head>
<body style="background-color: #FCFCFC; font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:22px">
 

 
<div align="center" style="background-color: #FCFCFC">  
    <div style="width:700px; font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:22px">

        <div align="center">
            <p style="font-size:42px; padding-top: 20px"><b>Hi <%= @seller.name%>,</b></p>
            <p style="font-size:22px;">Congratulations! You sold your ticket(s) to <%= @order.event.name %>.</p>
        </div>
                
        <div align="center" style="padding-bottom:45px; padding-top: 20px; font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;">
            
            
            <style type="text/css">
.tg td{border-style:solid;border-width: 0px;}

</style>
                
            <table class="tg" cellspacing="0" style="border-width:0px;" height="999" width="572" background="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/dingoapp-prod/Email+images/Invoicev2.jpg">
              <tr>
                <td colspan="9" align="center" style="font-size: 35px; height: 185px; padding-bottom: 27px" valign="bottom" ><b>£<%= number_with_precision(@order.amount, :precision => 2) %></b></td>
              </tr> 
              <tr>
                <td style="width: 70px; height: 58px"></td>
                <td colspan="2"><b>Breakdown</b></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td></td>
                <td style="width: 45px;"></td>
                <td style="width: 212px; height: 58px">Event name:</td>
                <td colspan="4" style="padding-left: 38px"><%= @order.event.name %></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="height: 58px"></td>
                <td></td>
                <td>Number of tickets:</td>
                <td colspan="4" style="padding-left: 38px"><%= @order.num_tickets %></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="height: 58px"></td>
                <td></td>
                <td>Price per ticket:</td>
                <td colspan="4" style="padding-left: 38px">£<%= number_with_precision((@order.amount / @order.num_tickets), :precision => 2) %></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="height: 58px"></td>
                <td></td>
                <td style="padding-bottom: 0px"><b>Total:</b></td>
                <td colspan="4" style="padding-left: 38px"><b>£<%= number_with_precision(@order.amount, :precision => 2) %></b></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="height: 150px"></td>
                <td></td>
                <td valign="top" style="padding-left: 35px; padding-top: 30px"><div><img style="border-radius: 108px; border:3px solid grey;" src="http://graph.facebook.com/v2.0/<%= @buyer.fb_id%>/picture?redirect=1&height=200&type=normal&width=200" height="108" width="108"></div></td>
                <td colspan="4" valign="top" style="padding-top: 20px"><p><b>Buyer Name:</b></p><p style="font-size: 25px"><%= @buyer.name%></p></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="9" style="font-size: 18px; height: 110px; text-align: center; padding-top: 30px" valign="top" >Please arrange delivery of the ticket(s) with the buyer.<p>Remember to use Dingo's in-app chat.</p></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="9" style="font-size: 12px; color: grey; text-align: center; padding-bottom: 20px" valign="bottom" >Order ID: <%= @order.id %></td>
              </tr>                            
            </table>
        </div>

        <div align="center">
            <p style="padding-bottom:15px; font-size:22px"><b>Important information about your money</b></p>
            <p style="padding-bottom:35px; font-size:22px;">Your money will be available <b><u>48 hours</u></b> after the event takes place. Dingo will hold the money in the meantime to ensure security for both parties.</p>
            <p style="padding-bottom:35px; font-size:22px">If you have logged in with PayPal already we will make the transfer directly into your account. You can login to PayPal in the app at any point to update your information.</p>
            <p style="padding-bottom:35px; font-size:22px">If you have not logged in or don't have a PayPal account, we will send you another email when your money is available explaining how to withdraw it.</p>
            <hr >
            <p style="padding-bottom:35px; padding-top: 20px; font-size:22px">If you have any questions or feedback, or need to cancel the transaction, please get in touch by email: <a href="mailto:info@dingoapp.co.uk">info@dingoapp.co.uk</a>.</p>
            <p style="padding-bottom:35px; font-size:22px">Remember to follow us on Twitter to see some of the latest tickets on sale <a href="https://twitter.com/Dingotickets" target="_blank">@dingotickets</a>.</p>
            <p style="padding-bottom:35px; font-size:22px">Thanks for using our service.</p>
            <p style="padding-bottom:35px; font-size:22px">Dingo</p>
        </div>
        

        <div align="center" style="padding-bottom:35px"><a href="http://bit.ly/DingoAppEmails" target="_blank"><img src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/dingoapp-prod/Email+images/appstoreicon.jpg"></a> </div>

        
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td><div align="center"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/dingoapp" target="_blank"><img height="50px" width="50px" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/dingoapp-prod/Email+images/Facebook+Square.jpg"></a> </div></td>
                <td><div align="center"><a href="https://twitter.com/Dingotickets" target="_blank"><img height="50px" width="50px" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/dingoapp-prod/Email+images/Twitter+square.jpg"></a> </div></td>
            </tr>
        </table>    

        
    </div>
</div>  
</body>
</html>














